  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Roast the eggplant for 30 minutes or until the skin is charred and blistered.",
    "Let the eggplant cool down, then peel off the skin and place it in a blender.",
    "Add the canned tuna, fish sauce, honey, lemon juice, garlic, paprika, and salt to the blender.",
    "Blend the mixture until smooth and creamy.",
    "With the blender running, slowly pour in the olive oil through the top.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the Sweetened Middle Eastern Fish Ganouesh with pita chips or vegetables."
